# MISC::GET_IS_AUTO_SAVE_OFF

## Summary
Returns TRUE if the autosave option has been turned off in the game's frontend

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns true if profile setting 208 is equal to 0.
